notepad .gitignore
```

Click **Yes** when Notepad asks to create a new file.

Paste this inside:
```
# Frontend
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/build/
frontend/.env

# Backend
backend/target/
backend/.env
backend/*.jar

# AI Service
ai_service/__pycache__/
ai_service/venv/
ai_service/.env
ai_service/*.pyc

# General
.DS_Store
*.log